snippet.title: Levels+: Addictive Puzzle Game Nintendo Switch Gameplay
snippet.description:
Hey everyone! :D Check out the first 20+ minutes of Levels+: Addictive Puzzle Game which comes to the Nintendo eShop TOMORROW for Europe and America. This game is now available in Japan. A massive thank you to Shumpei Hayashi and the team at flow for the code so I could put up content of their game :D This game is quite the challenge and can keep you at your screen for ages :D Like what you see? Make sure to check it out on the Nintendo Switch Shop! :D

Follow flow on Social Media too:
http://sickman.me/
https://twitter.com/shayashi23
